      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON GIN (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (22.87) in a Grade 5 at Ballarat. Should be very hard to beat this time. TIPSY TILLY (1) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from six tries. Below best last time at Shepparton (22.93) in a Grade 5, finishing a 8 length eighth. Looks one of the chances. CANYA IGNITE (4) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at Healesville in a handy 19.63 beating Red Cabang. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature again. STELLA ROSE (8) boasts a solid strike-rate from this box.",
